TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed HttpStatusCode extends System.Enum

summary.span: 包含为 HTTP 定义的状态代码的值。

span.span: Contains the values of status codes defined for HTTP.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 枚举包含 RFC 2616 中为 HTTP 1.1 定义的状态代码的值。The enumeration contains the values of the status codes defined in RFC 2616 for HTTP 1.1. HTTP 请求的状态包含在 属性中。The status of an HTTP request is contained in the property. 如果 属性为 `false` ，则以下枚举值会引发异常：If the property is `false`, the following enumeration values cause an exception to be thrown: - `Ambiguous` - `Found` - `MultipleChoices` - `Redirect` - `RedirectKeepVerb` - `RedirectMethod` - `SeeOther` - `TemporaryRedirect` ## Examples 下面的示例将由返回的状态 与类的成员进行比较 ，以确定响应的状态。The following example compares the status returned by an with a member of the class to determine the status of a response. [!code-cpp[Classic HttpStatusCode Example#1](~/samples/snippets/cpp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/Classic HttpStatusCode Example/CPP/source.cpp#1)] [!code-csharp[Classic HttpStatusCode Example#1](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/Classic HttpStatusCode Example/CS/source.cs#1)] [!code-vb[Classic HttpStatusCode Example#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_Remoting/Classic HttpStatusCode Example/VB/source.vb#1)]
